ay","title":"我还是没有忘记，真正的美好是什么","excerpt":"陪一个人，画一幅画，写篇文章，分享一些东西，跳一场舞。","content":"<p><span>陪一个人，画一幅画，写篇文章，分享一些东西，跳一场舞。</span></p>\n<p><span>一次又一次的思考，偶偶然然的清醒，花了太多时间，去寻找身边的美好</span></p>\n<p><span>别放弃，请珍惜</span></p>\n","slug":"5d61640520bd4a483894f4ca","prev":[{"ID":383333,"title":"评价ui设计作品好坏的八个标准(界面/交互设计研究)","excerpt":"一套完整的UI设计其实是比较复杂的，从需求分析到市场定位，从草稿到拟方案，从创意元素的组合到想法沉淀，从设计规范到突破传统，从纸上到电脑上，从个人到团队，或者从团队到个人，从素材收集到素材处理，从0思路到偶然，等等，其实设计一个东西真的真的会碰到太多太多的问题，这么复杂的过程，做出来的东西，其实别人看到的都只是“表面”，设计者也不会将自己内心真正的东西暴露出来，因此大多数人不能完完全全理解一个作品","slug":"a1fabd365958f7bb2ab422b9","post_date":"2014-11-10 13:53:53","post_date_gmt":"2014-11-10 13:53:53","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_3224f82149efa7d572d8f38f-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfefaddffxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_3224f82149efa7d572d8f38f-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfefaddffxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_3224f82149efa7d572d8f38f-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfefaddffxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":403333,"title":"曾经，我迷于选择，现在，我衷于选择。","excerpt":"曾经，我迷于选择，现在，我衷于选择。","slug":"7c4e8a4757d1c2ce9fa20f93","post_date":"2015-05-29 01:29:28","post_date_gmt":"2015-05-29 01:29:28","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_d8732e1b6a3d8b2b34b594c4-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdebadbbbcxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_d8732e1b6a3d8b2b34b594c4-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdebadbbbcxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_d8732e1b6a3d8b2b34b594c4-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdebadbbbcxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2015-02-01 23:08:09","post_date_gmt":"2015-02-01 23:08:09","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2015-02-01 23:08:09","post_modified_gmt":"2